{"type": "article", "id": 3250, "title": "Menu 玻璃茶壶", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-04T08:08:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232917PEuie2bqpNsf3o1x.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t瑞士设计团队 Norm 为丹麦家居品牌 Menu 设计了一款茶壶，整个壶身皆用玻璃材质制成，显得晶莹剔透，搭配独特的茶胆设计，让你可以轻松冲泡一壶茶香，自在品茗。冲泡后，利用橡胶提把轻松拉起茶叶，可轻松掌握茶水的浓度。Norm 为壶盖选取了塑料材质，这是为了避免重复盖取时，造成玻璃连续碰撞，容易碎裂。定价 49.99 美元，<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B004U8ZL2U?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=wiredte-20\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232916O4UnZcaBrWXVxkSu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232916aoZ39M6HTAWFzyse.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1828125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}